The '''1988 Monte Carlo Open''' (also known as the '''Volvo Monte Carlo Open''' for sponsorship reasons) was a men's [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Clay court|outdoor clay courts]] at the [[Monte Carlo Country Club]] in [[Monte Carlo]], [[Monaco]]<ref name="info"/> that was part of the [[1988 Nabisco Grand Prix]]. The tournament was held from 18 April through 24 April 1989.<ref name="info"/>

==Champions==
===Singles===
{{main|1988 Monte Carlo Open – Singles}}
{{flagicon|TCH}} '''[[Ivan Lendl]]''' defeated {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Martín Jaite]], 5–7, 6–4, 7–5, 6–3

===Doubles===
{{main|1988 Monte Carlo Open – Doubles}}
{{flagicon|ESP}} '''[[Sergio Casal]]''' / {{flagicon|ESP}} '''[[Emilio Sánchez]]''' defeated {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Henri Leconte]] / {{flagicon|TCH}} [[Ivan Lendl]], 6–1, 6–3

