'''Cesare Attolini''' is a luxury [[menswear]] brand founded in [[Naples]] the 1930s by Vincenzo Attolini. The brand is now run by his grandsons Giuseppe and Massimiliano Attolini.<ref>Matt Sebra, ''GQ'' magazine [https://www.gq.com/story/first-look-cesare-attolini-opens-its-doors-on-madison-ave First Look: Cesare Attolini Opens Its Doors on Madison Ave.] March 16, 2012</ref> Attolini helped to promote the Neapolitan silhouette featuring slim lines, high armholes, and soft-shouldered jackets.<ref>''New York'' magazine, [http://nymag.com/listings/stores/cesare-attolini/ Cesare Attolini: Critic's Pick]</ref>
Retail locations are in Naples, Milan, Miami, New York City, Baku, and Istanbul.<ref>[http://cesareattolini.com/show-rooms/ Official site]</ref>
