The '''Dutch Waterski Association''' ({{lang-nl|Nederlandse Waterski Bond}}, '''NWB''') is a [[Trade union|union]] of all [[Netherlands|Dutch]] [[water skiing|water ski]], [[wakeboarding|wakeboard]], [[cable skiing]] and [[water sports]] clubs and organisations. The association's goal is to promote the sport of water skiing and wakeboarding. It organises competition, subsidies, training and scouting, and coordinates sending skiers to international sport events.
The Dutch Waterski Association is a member organization of the [[International Water Ski Federation]].
