'''Galați TV Tower''' ({{lang-ro|Turnul de televiziune Galaţi}}) is a {{Convert|150|m|ft|adj=on}} tall concrete [[tower]] used for [[FM broadcasting|FM]] and TV [[broadcasting]] in [[Galați]], [[Romania]]. The tower, completed in 1978, is equipped with a tower restaurant, perhaps the only of this kind in Romania.

